The exhibition "Brilliance of time -- CiÂ·Park" kicked off in Beijing on Wednesday. The exhibition incorporates modern cross-media technologies and the most advanced digital tools to make history come alive. Five lovely animal characters are created specially for it. Hosted by Xinhuanet. Co., Ltd and co-hosted by the Jingdezhen Municipal People's Government of Jiangxi Province, the exhibition will run from June 5 to August 31 in Beijing, the first stop of the exhibition. It will be held in other Chinese cities later this year. Nearly 100 guests, including heads of relevant departments, representatives of culture and fine arts industry, media representatives attended the ceremony. 
